<br>
Some of the other changes they have made:<br>
<br>
NPC's that cast can now cast spells higher than their level.<br>
They can't be interrupted like we can when we cast.<br>
<br>
In some cases, I have heard of greens killing people very fast, so be on your guard.<br>
<br>
Supposedly there is some balancing that will be happening, but for now it is a much more dangerous world.<br>
<br>
Naz <p>Nazonidus Ashurbanipal
